## 1. STACK 7 LAYER — DISCIPLINE BAT[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] BUOC[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME]

Nauion render PHAI[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] tuen[C0:RN_AN_EN] thu[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] stack 7 layer, dung[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] thu[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] tu[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME], khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] skip, khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] dao[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME]:

