LAYER 6: Text                                    ← solid, KHONG[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] glow tren[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] text
LAYER 5: Specular Edge / Fresnel Rim            ← chi[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] o[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] goc[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] nghieng[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME]
LAYER 4: Core Emission + Event Horizon          ← MOT[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] diem[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] seng[C1:RN_ANG_ENG] duy nhat[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME]
LAYER 3: Lua[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] Diffuse (silk scatter)             ← ten[C1:RN_AN_EN] xa[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] co[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] kiem[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] soat[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME]
LAYER 2: Glass Petals (refraction)               ← trong suot[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME], KHONG[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] inner glow
LAYER 1: Background Texture (galaxy/noise)      ← opacity ≤ 0.15
LAYER 0: Solid Black (#010101)                   ← non-negotiable
```

### 1.1. LAYER 0 — Solid Black `#010101`

**Bat[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] buoc[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME]:** Background phai[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] la[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] den[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] tuyet[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] dau[C1:RN_OI_AU] hoac[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] gen[C2:RN_AN_EN] tuyet[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] dau[C1:RN_OI_AU] (`#010101`, `#000000`).

**Ly[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] do vat[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] ly[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME]:** De[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] thay[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] duoc[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] khuc[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] xa[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] va[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] ten[C1:RN_AN_EN] xa[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME], anh[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] seng[C1:RN_ANG_ENG] phai[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] co[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] **nen[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] tau[C1:RN_OI_AU] tham chieu[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME]**. Pastel BG → mat[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] kha[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] neng[C0:RN_ANG_ENG] quan sat[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] hien[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] tuong[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] quang hoc[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] → over-ray tu[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] xay[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] ra.

**Vi pham[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] dien[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] hinh[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME]:** Dat[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] pastel/gradient mau[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] lam[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] background → rau[C0:RN_OI_AU] ngay vao[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] sai vat[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] ly[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME].

```css
/* ✅ DUNG[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] */
