**Bat[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] buoc[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME]:** Day[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] la[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] **chia[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] khoa[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] Nauion**. Lop[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] lua[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] diffuse la[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] thu[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] tao[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] nen[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] cam[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] giac[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] "pastel mong[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] veng[C2:RN_ANG_ENG] soft".

