**Ly[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] do vat[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] ly[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME]:** Day[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] la[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] mau[C0:RN_OI_AU] truong[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] ten[C1:RN_AN_EN] xa[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] co[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] kiem[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] soat[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] — nhu[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] suong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] mong[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME]. Ten[C1:RN_AN_EN] xa[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] lam[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] anh[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] seng[C1:RN_ANG_ENG] "tham[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME]" thay vi[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] "chay[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME]". Neu[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] thieu[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] lua[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] diffuse → glass qua[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] kho[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME], anh[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] seng[C1:RN_ANG_ENG] qua[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] gat[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME]. Neu[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] lua[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] qua[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] dam[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] → ten[C1:RN_AN_EN] xa[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] vo[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] hen[C5:RN_AN_EN], mat[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] chieu[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] sau[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME].

```css
/* ✅ DUNG[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] — lua[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] dung[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] nong[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] do[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] + blend */
.silk-diffuse {
